[Student "S"]
{When SOUTH agrees to \Ss, NORTH will not stop short of a slam. 
The RKCB 4NT bid tells NORTH that they have all five Key Cards since SOUTH could hardly 
have a 2\C opening hand with no Aces.

NORTH's 5\H bid is the Queen Ask, and SOUTH's reply confirms that she holds 
the \SQ, and also has the \CK.

NORTH figures the \S suit will run, and this should be enough for Grand Slam. He chooses 7NT.}

