[Student "S"]
{EAST knows there are enough points for slam, but she is worried about the trump suit. 
WEST's support doesn't guarantee more than three \Ss, and if they are not headed 
by the Queen she could lose a trump trick.

Her RKCB bid relieves her mind when EAST claims two Key Cards PLUS the \SQ. 
She bids 6\S (and hopes for a 3-2 trump split!).}

