[Student "S"]
{NORTH has 21 points, and when she hears SOUTH make a limit raise she tries for slam with RKCB.

SOUTH answers with just one Key Card so NORTH stops at 5\S, knowing they are missing 
two Key Cards.

Of course she didn't expect the two missing Key Cards to be the Ace and King of trumps!}

